title: Second Opinion Reader needed
body:
Not a beta, truly just a second opinion for a fanfic. I started it, got lost and now I am not sure about its coherency and whether I should or should not rewrite it completely. 

If you have a bit of time on your hands, like to be brutally honest and want to help this disaster of a human with a fanfic, please DM me! I shall be most grateful until my dying days.

summary: OOF oh jeez okay, so it’s been a little while since I drew Moomin related art, and wowzas, I’ve actually changed my style a bit....
body:
OOF oh jeez okay, so it’s been a little while since I drew Moomin related art, and wowzas, I’ve actually changed my style a bit. I’m still trying to get used to it, but I’m very happy with the direction my art is going :) it’s been a while since I felt that way. 


for commissions, look at my commission info page and then pm me on here or email me at skittzune@gmail.com :D
